OL,3,CCould Loch Ness be turned into a giant
OL,4,Cwater battery?
OL,6,FITV News Science Correspondent Martin
OL,7,FStew visits Switzerland to find out
OL,8,Fwhether Scotland can adopt its newest
OL,9,Fhydro pump technology
OL,11,FDid you know the Loch Ness holds more
OL,12,Fwater than all the rivers, lakes and
OL,13,Freservoirs in England and Wales
OL,14,Fcombined?
OL,16,FWhat if you could use that natural
OL,17,Fresource to store the energy created
OL,18,Fby renewables?
