OL,3,CCould Loch Ness be turned into a giant
OL,4,Cwater battery?
OL,6,FTo see how it works, I travelled to
OL,7,FNant de Drance in the Swiss Alps, a
OL,8,Fhydro pump storage "water battery"
OL,9,Fthat opened two years ago.
OL,11,FThe scale is enormous. Two reservoirs,
OL,12,Fone 500m higher than the other,
OL,13,Fconnected by a giant pipe channeled
OL,14,Fthrough the mountain.
OL,16,FTo get to the cavernous turbine
OL,17,Fchamber 600 metres underground, we had
OL,18,Fto drive through 6 kilometres of
OL,19,Ftunnels.
OL,21,FWhat is pump hydro storage?
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/9
