OL,3,CCould Loch Ness be turned into a giant
OL,4,Cwater battery?
OL,6,FProjects of this scale are usually
OL,7,Fgovernment funded but it's private
OL,8,Fcompanies taking the lead.
OL,10,FTo enable them to borrow the money to
OL,11,Fbuild, they're awaiting details of a
OL,12,F"cap and floor" scheme which would see
OL,13,Fthe government underwriting a minimum
OL,14,Fincome.
OL,16,FMr MacLeod told me Loch Ness is the
OL,17,Fideal place to build.
