OL,3,CCould Loch Ness be turned into a giant
OL,4,Cwater battery?
OL,6,F"The topology is ideally suited to
OL,7,Fthese projects with Lochs high up and
OL,8,FLochs low down and at the same time
OL,9,Fthis topology is situated right at the
OL,10,Fcentre between all of the wind power
OL,11,Fthat is being generated."
OL,13,FBut what about the environmental
OL,14,Fimpact? Loch Ness is a site world
OL,15,Frenowned for its beauty.
