OL,3,CCould Loch Ness be turned into a giant
OL,4,Cwater battery?
OL,6,F"It shouldn't look any different at
OL,7,Fall from the Loch itself" Mr MacLeod
OL,8,Ftold me. "You might see from certain
OL,9,Fangles the dam. The dam itself is like
OL,10,Fa continuation of the hill so it will
OL,11,Fbe covered with grass and heather and
OL,12,Fwill disappear fairly quickly."
OL,14,FCritics are also worried about the
OL,15,Fimpact fluctuating water levels could
OL,16,Fhave on fish stocks. Engineers from
OL,17,FGlenn Earrach's project say water
OL,18,Flevels wouldn't move more than a foot.
OL,20,FThe UK government is committed to
OL,21,Fdecarbonising power production by 2035.
